'''腕隧道症候群'''（{{lang-en|Carpal tunnel syndrome}}），[[縮寫|縮寫]]：CTS）又稱'''腕道症候群'''、'''腕管综合症'''，俗稱'''滑鼠手'''，是指[[正中神經|正中神經]]在穿過[[腕|腕部]]的{{tsl|en|carpal tunnel|腕隧道}}處受到神經壓迫的疾病<ref name="Bur2014">{{Cite journal|title=Diagnosing and managing carpal tunnel syndrome in primary care|url=http://bjgp.org/lookup/doi/10.3399/bjgp14X679903|last=Burton|first=Claire|last2=Chesterton|first2=Linda S|date=2014-05|journal=British Journal of General Practice|issue=622|doi=10.3399/bjgp14X679903|volume=64|pages=262–263|language=en|issn=0960-1643|pmc=PMC4001168|pmid=24771836|last3=Davenport|first3=Graham}}</ref>。主要症狀為大拇指、食指、中指及無名指靠中指側會發生[[疼痛|疼痛]]、[[感覺減退|麻木感]]、{{le|刺痛感|Tingling}}<ref name="Bur2014" />，典型症狀通常是漸進式的，而且發生於晚上<ref name="NIH2016">{{cite web|title=Carpal Tunnel Syndrome Fact Sheet|url=http://www.ninds.nih.gov/disorders/carpal_tunnel/detail_carpal_tunnel.htm#227043049|accessdate=4 March  2016|date=January 28, 2016|website=National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181005/http://www.ninds.nih.gov/disorders/carpal_tunnel/detail_carpal_tunnel.htm#227043049|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。疼痛感可能延伸至手臂<ref name="NIH2016" />。患者抓握力量可能减弱且在長時間後[[大魚際肌|大魚際肌]]（拇指根部肌肉）会[[萎缩|萎缩]]<ref name="NIH2016" />。超過一半的病例是兩手都有症狀<ref name="Bur2014" />。<!-- 病因及診斷 Cause and diagnosis -->

風險因子包含[[肥胖症|肥胖]]、[[重複性勞損|腕部重複動作]]、[[妊娠|妊娠]]，以及[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]<ref name="AAOS2016">{{cite journal|title=Management of Carpal Tunnel Syndrome Evidence-Based Clinical Practice Guideline.|url=http://www.aaos.org/ctsguideline/|date=February 29, 2016|author1=American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Carpal tunnel syndrome in pregnancy.|first1=M|last2=Ilyas|first2=AM|date=October 2012|journal=The Orthopedic clinics of North America|issue=4|volume=43|pages=515-20|pmid=23026467|last3=Matzon|first3=JL|last1=Osterman}}</ref>。有初步的證據顯示[[甲狀腺機能低下症|甲狀腺機能低下症]]會增加患病風險<ref name="Shi2014">{{cite journal|title=Hypothyroidism and carpal tunnel syndrome: a meta-analysis.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_muscle-nerve_2014-12_50_6/page/879|first1=R|date=December 2014|journal=Muscle & nerve|issue=6|volume=50|pages=879-83|pmid=25204641|last1=Shiri}}</ref>。[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]與此病有輕度相關<ref name="AAOS2016" /><ref name="Padua2016">{{cite journal|title=Carpal tunnel syndrome: clinical features, diagnosis, and management|first1=L|last2=Coraci|first2=D|date=November 2016|journal=Lancet Neurology|issue=12|doi=10.1016/S1474-4422(16)30231-9|volume=15|pages=1273–84|type=Review|pmid=27751557|last3=Erra|first3=C|last4=Pazzaglia|first4=C|last5=Paolasso|first5=I|last6=Loreti|first6=C|last7=Caliandro|first7=P|last8=Hobson-Webb|first8=LD|last1=Padua}}</ref>。[[复合口服避孕药|复合口服避孕药]]目前顯示與此病無關。高風險職業包含電腦作業、操作震動機械，以及需要用力抓握的工作<ref name="AAOS2016" />。根據病徵、症狀和特定的[[理學檢查|理學檢查]]而懷疑有此症時，也許可藉{{tsl|en|electrodiagnostic test|電學檢查}}來確診<ref name="NIH2016" />。若拇指根部肌肉萎縮則可能罹患此症<ref name="AAOS2016" />。<!-- 預防與治療 Prevention and treatment -->

進行[[體能鍛煉|體能訓練]]可以降低腕隧道症候群的發生風險。症狀可以透過穿戴[[夾板|豎腕副木]]或是施打[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]獲得改善。使用[[非甾体抗炎药|非類固醇消炎藥]]或[[加巴喷丁|加巴喷丁]]並沒有效果。切斷[[橫腕韌帶|橫腕韌帶]]的外科手術效果，比一年的非手術治療效果來得更好。術後不需要再使用副木。沒有任何證據支持[[磁療|磁療]]有益<ref name="AAOS2016" />。<!-- 流行病學與預後 Epidemiology and prognosis -->

在美國大約有5%的人患有腕隧道症候群<ref>{{cite journal|title=Carpal tunnel syndrome.|first1=KD|date=January 2010|journal=The Journal of hand surgery|issue=1|volume=35|pages=147-52|pmid=20117319|last1=Bickel}}</ref>。通常發生於成人時期，而女性比男性更容易罹患<ref name="NIH2016" />，女性發生此疾病的比例為男性的3－10倍。超過33%的患者可以在沒有特別治療的情況下於約一年的時間後改善病況<ref name="Bur2014" />。腕隧道症候群的敘述初見於[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]<ref name="Amadio_2007">{{cite book|first=Peter C.|last=Amadio|editor1-first=Riccardo|editor1-last=Luchetti|editor2-first=Peter C.|editor2-last=Amadio|chapter=History of carpal tunnel syndrome|pages=3–9|chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=LMA3dh605bgC&pg=PA3|title=Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|publisher=Springer|location=Berlin|year=2007|isbn=978-3-540-22387-0}}</ref>。

== 症狀與徵象 ==
腕隧道症候群患者的[[大拇指|大拇指]]、[[食指|食指]]、[[中指|中指]]、以及[[無名指|無名指]]的橈側（靠中指側）會有[[感覺減退|麻木感]]、{{le|刺痛感|Tingling}}、或灼熱感，因為這個範圍的感覺和運動功能（肌肉控制）是由[[正中神經|正中神經]]支配。疼痛和不適感可能往近端延伸到前臂甚至上臂<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Carpal-tunnel-syndrome/Pages/Symptoms.aspx|title=Carpal tunnel syndrome – Symptoms|website={{le|NHS Choices|National Health Service (England)#Internet information service}}|accessdate=2016-05-21|dead-url = no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160524081418/http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Carpal-tunnel-syndrome/Pages/Symptoms.aspx|archivedate=2016-05-24}} Page last reviewed: 18/09/2014</ref>。低特異性的症狀可能包括手部或{{le|手腕疼痛|Wrist pain}}、握力下降<ref name=Atroshi_1999>{{cite journal |last1=Atroshi |first1=I. |last2=Gummesson |first2=C |last3=Johnsson |first3=R |last4=Ornstein |first4=E |last5=Ranstam |first5=J |last6=Rosén |first6=I |title=Prevalence of Carpal Tunnel Syndrome in a General Population |journal=JAMA |volume=282 |issue=2 |pages=153–158 |year=1999 |pmid=10411196 |doi=10.1001/jama.282.2.153}}</ref>、手部敏捷度下降<ref name="CTS_2009">{{cite web |title=Carpal Tunnel Syndrome Information Page |date=December 28, 2010 |publisher=National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke |url=http://www.ninds.nih.gov/disorders/carpal_tunnel/carpal_tunnel.htm |dead-url = no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101222221850/http://www.ninds.nih.gov/disorders/carpal_tunnel/carpal_tunnel.htm |archivedate=December 22, 2010 }}</ref>。

有些人認為正中神經症狀可以起因於{{le|胸廓出口|Thoracic outlet}}或前臂{{le|旋前圓肌|Pronator teres muscle}}兩頭之間的正中神經受到壓迫<ref>{{cite book|last=Netter|first=Frank|title=Atlas of Human Anatomy|url=https://archive.org/details/atlasofhumananat0000nett_w1j0|year=2011|publisher=Saunders Elsevier|location=Philadelphia, PA|isbn=978-0-8089-2423-4|pages=[https://archive.org/details/atlasofhumananat0000nett_w1j0/page/412 412], 417, 435|edition=5th}}</ref>，雖然這部分尚有爭論。

正中神經支配範圍的麻木感和{{le|感覺異常|Paresthesia}}是腕隧道{{le|神經壓迫症候群|Nerve compression syndrome}}標誌性的[[周邊神經病變|神經病變]]症狀<ref name="Padua2016"/>。如果不及時治療，可能會因為肌肉缺乏足夠的神經刺激，導致拇指肌肉無力和[[萎縮|萎縮]]<ref name="Padua2016"/>。通常不適感會在晚上和早晨時加重。

== 病因 ==
[[File:Carpal_Tunnel_Syndrome.png|thumb]]穿過與手指肌腱共用的狹窄空間]]
大多數病例為[[病因不明症|病因不明]]<ref name="BOOSternbach_1999">{{cite journal|title=The carpal tunnel syndrome|first1=G|journal=Journal of Emergency Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.1016/S0736-4679(99)00030-X|year=1999|volume=17|pages=519–23|pmid=10338251|last1=Sternbach}}</ref>。風險因子包括[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]、[[重複性勞損|手腕過度使用]]、[[妊娠|妊娠]]、[[遺傳|遺傳]]、[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]<ref name="AAOS2016" /><ref name="Ost2012" /><ref name="Loz2008" />。有初步的證據顯示[[甲狀腺機能低下症|甲狀腺機能低下症]]會增加患病風險<ref name="Shi2014" />。[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]與此病則呈現輕度相關<ref name="AAOS2016" /><ref name="Padua2016" />。使用[[複合口服避孕藥|複合口服避孕藥]]不會影響患病風險<ref name="AAOS2016" />。高風險職業包含電腦作業、操作震動機械、需要用力抓握的工作<ref name="AAOS2016" />。

創傷<ref name="Katz_2002">{{cite journal|title=Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|first1=Jeffrey N.|last2=Simmons|first2=Barry P.|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|issue=23|doi=10.1056/NEJMcp013018|year=2002|volume=346|pages=1807–12|pmid=12050342|last1=Katz}}</ref>和[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]<ref name="Carpal Tunnel Syndrome">{{cite web|title=Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|url=http://orthoinfo.aaos.org/topic.cfm?topic=a00005|date=December 2009|publisher=American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927054213/http://orthoinfo.aaos.org/topic.cfm?topic=A00005|archivedate=2011-09-27|deadurl=no}}</ref>也可能與腕隧道症候群相關。

== 診斷 ==
專家共識已將正中神經支配範圍的麻木感、夜間症狀、肌肉無力或萎縮、{{le|腕隧道|Carpal tunnel}}處提內耳氏徵象陽性、感覺檢查異常（例如{{le|兩點區辨覺|Two-point discrimination}}）標準化列為臨床診斷標準<ref>{{cite journal|title=Consensus criteria for the classification of carpal tunnel syndrome in epidemiologic studies|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-public-health_1998-10_88_10/page/1447|last=Rempel|first=D|journal=Am J Public Health|issue=10|doi=10.2105/AJPH.88.10.1447|year=1998|volume=88|pages=1447–1451|pmc=1508472|pmid=9772842|author3=Amadio PC|display-authors=etal|author2=Evanoff B}}</ref><ref name="Graham consensus">{{cite journal|title=Development and validation of diagnostic criteria for carpal tunnel syndrome|last=Graham|first=B|journal=Journal of Hand Surgery|issue=6|year=2006|volume=31A|pages=919–924|pmid=16886290|author3=Naglie G|author4=Wright JG|author2=Regehr G}}</ref>。疼痛也可以是症狀之一，儘管不如感覺異常那麼常見。

=== 理學檢查 ===
儘管已廣泛地使用，但如果斐倫式試驗法、提內耳氏徵象、輕彈徵象（{{lang|en|Flick sign}}）、上肢神經檢查等項目僅其中之一為陽性，並不足以作為診斷<ref name="AAOS2016" />。
* {{le|斐倫式試驗法|Phalen maneuver}}，輕柔地屈曲手腕到極限，保持此姿勢並等待症狀是否誘發出來<ref name="Harrison">{{cite book|vauthors=Cush JJ, Lipsky PE|chapter=Approach to articular and musculoskeletal disorders|title=Harrison's Principles of Internal Medicine|edition=16th|page=2035|publisher=McGraw-Hill Professional|year=2004|isbn=978-0-07-140235-4}}</ref>。如果60秒內產生[[正中神經|正中神經]]支配範圍麻木感，則為陽性。麻木感越早開始，表示病情越嚴重，前瞻性研究顯示目前僅有斐倫式試驗法與腕隧道症候群的嚴重程度有相關<ref name="uptodate.com">{{cite web|title=Treatment of carpal tunnel syndrome|url=http://www.uptodate.com/patients/content/topic.do?topicKey=~wx2xecoDuYz0gp|date=October 5, 2009|publisher=[[UpToDate|UpToDate]]|first1=Kevin R.|last1=Scott|first2=Milind J.|last2=Kothari}}</ref>。在不同的研究中，斐倫式試驗法的數據有所不同，靈敏度從42%到85%不等，而特異度在54%到98%之間<ref name="Padua2016" /> 。
* [[提內耳氏徵象|提內耳氏徵象]]，正中神經的經典檢測方式，輕敲[[橫腕韌帶|橫腕韌帶]]上的皮膚以誘發正中神經支配範圍的疼痛或感覺異常。根據研究，提內耳氏徵象用於診斷腕隧道症候群具有38-100%的靈敏度和55-100%的特異度<ref name="Padua2016" /> 。
* [[德爾坎測試|德爾坎測試]]，施測者以拇指對腕隧道加壓30秒<ref name="Carpal Compression Test">{{Citation|title=Carpal Compression Test|url=http://www.fpnotebook.com/Ortho/Exam/CrplCmprsnTst.htm|year=2008|accessdate=2010-05-04}}</ref>，若受試者感受到疼痛或正中神經支配部分{{tsl|en|paresthesia|感覺異常}}即為陽性<ref name="Gonzalez_1997">{{Cite journal|title=Value of the carpal compression test in the diagnosis of carpal tunnel syndrome|first=J|last2=Delgadomartinez|first2=A|journal=The Journal of Hand Surgery: Journal of the British Society for Surgery of the Hand|issue=1|doi=10.1016/S0266-7681(97)80012-5|year=1997|volume=22|pages=38–41|pmid=9061521|last3=Gonzalezgonzalez|first3=I|last4=Lovic|first4=A|last1=Gonzalezdelpino}}</ref><ref name="Durkan_1991">{{Cite journal|title=A new diagnostic test for carpal tunnel syndrome|first=JA|journal=The Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume|issue=4|doi=10.2106/00004623-199173040-00009|year=1991|volume=73|pages=535–8|pmid=1796937|last1=Durkan}}</ref>。
* 舉手測試（{{lang|en|Hand elevation test}}），將雙手舉高過頭，如果在2分鐘內正中神經支配範圍的症狀再現，則為陽性。舉手測試比提內耳氏徵象、斐倫式試驗法、腕壓迫測試具有更高的[[靈敏度和特異度|靈敏度和特異度]]，[[卡方檢驗|卡方統計分析]]顯示與提內耳氏徵象、斐倫式試驗法、腕壓迫測試同樣有效或甚至更好<ref>{{cite journal|title=The diagnostic assessment of hand elevation test in carpal tunnel syndrome|date=November 2012|journal=Journal of Korean Neurosurgical Society|issue=5|doi=10.3340/jkns.2012.52.5.472|volume=52|pages=472–5|pmc=3539082|pmid=23323168|vauthors=Ma H, Kim I}}</ref>。

需要特別注意：真正患有腕隧道症候群（壓迫腕隧道內的正中神經）的患者，其[[大魚際肌|大魚際肌]]（拇指根部的肌肉隆起）不會有感覺喪失，這是因為正中神經的掌側分支會支配該區域，此分支並未進入腕隧道內<ref>{{cite book|last=Netter|first=Frank|title=Atlas of Human Anatomy|url=https://archive.org/details/atlasofhumananat0000nett_w1j0|year=2011|publisher=Saunders Elsevier|location=Philadelphia, PA|isbn=978-0-8089-2423-4|page=[https://archive.org/details/atlasofhumananat0000nett_w1j0/page/447 447]|edition=5th}}</ref>。正中神經的這個特徵可以幫助將腕隧道症候群與[[胸廓出口症候群|胸廓出口症候群]]或{{le|旋前圓肌症候群|Pronator teres syndrome}}區分開來。

=== 電學診斷 ===
因為有些情況可能被誤診為腕隧道症候群，如果病史和理學檢查有所懷疑，有時會利用{{le|神經傳導檢查|Nerve conduction study}}和[[肌電圖|肌電圖]]進行{{le|電學診斷|Electrodiagnostic medicine}}。以神經傳導檢查來確認診斷尚有爭議<ref name="Padua2016" />。有多種電學診斷測試可用於診斷腕隧道症候群，但是[[靈敏度和特異度|靈敏度和特異度]]最高、最可靠的方式是採用綜合感覺指數（{{lang|en|Combined Sensory Index}}），也稱為魯賓遜指數（{{lang|en|Robinson index}}）<ref name="Robinson_2007">{{cite journal|title=Electrodiagnosis of Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|first1=L|journal=Physical Medicine and Rehabilitation Clinics of North America|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.pmr.2007.07.008|year=2007|volume=18|pages=733–46|pmid=17967362|last1=Robinson}}</ref>。神經壓迫導致[[髓鞘|髓鞘]]的破壞，電學診斷上的表現為[[延遲_(工程學)|延遲]]增長和{{le|神經傳導速度|Nerve conduction velocity}}減慢<ref name="uptodate.com" />，但是電學診斷結果正常並不能排除腕隧道症候群，因為神經損傷必須達到[[閾值|閾值]]才會使檢查發現異常，而且異常值是可變的<ref name="Graham consensus" /> 。

=== 影像檢查 ===
使用[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振檢查]]或[[醫學超音波檢查|超音波檢查]]診斷腕隧道症候群的效益尚不明朗<ref name="Wilder-Smith_2006">{{cite journal|title=Diagnosing carpal tunnel syndrome—clinical criteria and ancillary tests|first1=Einar P|last2=Seet|first2=Raymond C S|journal=Nature Clinical Practice Neurology|issue=7|doi=10.1038/ncpneuro0216|year=2006|volume=2|pages=366–74|pmid=16932587|last3=Lim|first3=Erle C H|last1=Wilder-Smith}}</ref><ref name="Bland_2005">{{cite journal|title=Carpal tunnel syndrome|first1=Jeremy DP|journal=Current Opinion in Neurology|issue=5|doi=10.1097/01.wco.0000173142.58068.5a|year=2005|volume=18|pages=581–5|pmid=16155444|last1=Bland}}</ref><ref name="Jarvik_2004">{{cite journal|title=Diagnosis of carpal tunnel syndrome: electrodiagnostic and MR imaging evaluation|first1=J|last2=Yuen|first2=E|journal=Neuroimaging Clinics of North America|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.nic.2004.02.002|year=2004|volume=14|pages=93–102, viii|pmid=15177259|last3=Kliot|first3=M|last1=Jarvik}}</ref>，不建議常規使用<ref name="AAOS2016" />。核磁共振檢查具有高靈敏度，但特異度低，其影像中的高信號強度可顯現[[軸突|軸突]]的變化和髓鞘的退化或水腫<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Carpal Tunnel Syndrome: Symptoms, Causes and Treatment Options. Literature Reviev|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/28436376|last=Zamborsky|first=Radoslav|last2=Kokavec|first2=Milan|date=2017-01-26|journal=Ortopedia, Traumatologia, Rehabilitacja|issue=1|doi=10.5604/15093492.1232629|volume=19|pages=1–8|issn=2084-4336|pmid=28436376|last3=Simko|first3=Lukas|last4=Bohac|first4=Martin}}</ref>。

=== 鑑別診斷 ===
[[神經根病變|頸椎神經根病變]]也可引起手和腕部的感覺異常或疼痛，可能被誤認為腕隧道症候群，但前者的症狀通常始於[[頸部|頸部]]，並沿著患側手臂向下延伸，並可能隨著頸部的活動使症狀更加明顯<ref name="Padua2016" />。頸椎的肌電圖和影像檢查可以幫忙區分頸椎神經根病變與腕隧道症候群<ref name="Padua2016" />。腕隧道症候群常有感覺異常，如果疼痛是主要症狀，腕隧道症候群會比較不像是病源<ref name="Graham 2587–2593">{{cite journal|title=The Value Added by Electrodiagnostic Testing in the Diagnosis of Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|last=Graham|first=B.|date=1 December 2008|journal=The Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery|issue=12|doi=10.2106/JBJS.G.01362|volume=90|pages=2587–2593|pmid=19047703}}</ref>。

== 治療 ==
普遍接受的治療包括：[[物理治療|物理治療]]、口服或局部注射[[類固醇|類固醇]]、[[副木|副木]]、[[手術|手術]]減壓腕橫韌帶<ref name="Piaz2007">{{cite journal|title=A systematic review of conservative treatment of carpal tunnel syndrome|last=Piazzini|first=DB|date=Apr 2007|journal=Clinical Rehabilitation|issue=4|doi=10.1177/0269215507077294|volume=21|pages=299–314|pmid=17613571|author3=Ferrara, PE|author4=Bertolini, C|author5=Tonali, P|author6=Maggi, L|author7=Rabini, A|author8=Piantelli, S|author9=Padua, L|author2=Aprile, I}}</ref>。有限的證據顯示[[加巴噴丁|加巴噴丁]]並不比安慰劑有效<ref name="Padua2016" />。沒有足夠的證據證明[[治療性超音波|治療性超音波]]、[[瑜伽|瑜伽]]、[[針灸|針灸]]、{{le|低功率雷射|Low-level laser therapy}}、[[維生素B6|維生素B6]]、運動等有益於腕隧道症候群<ref name="Padua2016" /><ref name="Piaz2007" />。日常活動的改變可能避免症狀惡化<ref name="Carpal Tunnel Syndrome" />。

{{le|美國骨科醫學會|American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons}}建議先嘗試進行至少一個療程的[[保守治療|保守治療]]，才考慮減壓手術<ref name="aaos2007">{{cite book|date=September 2008|title=Clinical Practice Guideline on the Treatment of Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|publisher=American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons|url=http://www.aaos.org/Research/guidelines/CTSTreatmentGuideline.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091211112335/http://www.aaos.org/research/guidelines/CTSTreatmentGuideline.pdf|archivedate=2009-12-11|access-date=2010-06-27}}{{Page needed|date=January 2011}}</ref>。如果當前的治療方法無法在2到7週內解除症狀，則應嘗試其他治療方法。如果有證據顯示患者正中神經出現{{le|去神經化|Denervation}}或患者願意選擇直接手術治療，則可早期進行手術。如果患者有[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、[[頸椎|頸椎]][[神經根病變|神經根病變]]、[[甲狀腺機能低下症|甲狀腺機能低下症]]、{{le|多發性神經病變|Polyneuropathy}}、[[妊娠|妊娠]]、[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]、或腕隧道症候群起因於工作等狀況，建議的治療方式可能有所不同<ref name="aaos2007" />。

=== 副木 ===
[[Image:Carpal_tunnel_splint.jpg|thumb]]可保持手腕伸直]]
[[File:Karpaltunnelsyndrom-Orthese_aussen.JPG|thumb]]
腕部[[裝具|裝具]]和[[副木|副木]]的重要性眾所周知，但許多患者不願意使用。1993年，{{le|美國神經醫學會|American Academy of Neurology}}建議發病早期就給予非侵入性治療，亦即使用副木治療輕度和中度的腕隧道症候群，除非感覺或運動神經損傷或肌電圖報告顯示病情嚴重<ref name="American_Academy_Neurology_1993">{{cite journal|title=Quality Standards Subcommittee: Practice parameter for carpal tunnel syndrome|author=American Academy of Neurology|journal=Neurology|issue=11|doi=10.1212/wnl.43.11.2406|year=2006|volume=43|pages=2406–2409|pmid=8232968}}</ref>。 

為了獲得最佳效果，許多醫療專業人員建議夜晚休息期間配戴副木。可能的話，在造成手腕壓力的活動期間也可戴上副木<ref name="Premoselli_2006">{{cite journal|title=Neutral wrist splinting in carpal tunnel syndrome: a 3- and 6-months clinical and neurophysiologic follow-up evaluation of night-only splint therapy|first1=S|last2=Sioli|first2=P|journal=Europa Medicophysica|issue=2|year=2006|volume=42|pages=121–6|pmid=16767058|last3=Grossi|first3=A|last4=Cerri|first4=C|last1=Premoselli}}</ref><ref name="Michlovitz_2004">{{cite journal|title=Conservative interventions for carpal tunnel syndrome|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-orthopaedic-and-sports-physical-therapy_2004-10_34_10/page/589|first1=SL|journal=The Journal of Orthopaedic and Sports Physical Therapy|issue=10|doi=10.2519/jospt.2004.34.10.589|year=2004|volume=34|pages=589–600|pmid=15552705|last1=Michlovitz}}</ref>。通常不在白天使用副木，因為需要讓腕部活動以避免關節僵硬並防止肌肉弱化<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK279596/|title=Carpal tunnel syndrome: Wrist splints and hand exercises|last=Institute for Quality and Efficiency in Health Care|date=November 16, 2017|publisher=Institute for Quality and Efficiency in Health Care (IQWiG)}}</ref>。

=== 皮質類固醇 ===
局部注射[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]可以有效的暫時緩解症狀<ref name="pmid17443508">{{cite journal|title=Local corticosteroid injection for carpal tunnel syndrome|first1=Shawn C|last2=Tardif|first2=Gaetan|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=2|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD001554.pub2|year=2007|pages=CD001554|pmid=17443508|last3=Ashworth|first3=Nigel L|last4=Marshall|first4=Shawn C|editor1-last=Marshall|editor1-first=Shawn C|last1=Marshall}}</ref>。一般認為這種治療方式可以減少正中神經的腫脹，從而減輕患者的不適<ref name="Padua2016" />。注射時使用[[医学超声检查|超音波導引]]需要額外的費用支出，但可以更快地解除症狀<ref name="Padua2016" />。注射是在{{le|局部麻醉|Local anesthesia}}下進行<ref>{{cite web|title=Carpal Tunnel Steroid Injection|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/103333-overview#a4|accessdate=July 9, 2015|website=Medscape|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150729191652/http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/103333-overview#a4|archivedate=July 29, 2015|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Carpal Tunnel Injection Information|url=http://www.mountsinai.org/patient-care/health-library/treatments-and-procedures/carpal-tunnel-injection|publisher=EBSCO|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710145752/http://www.mountsinai.org/patient-care/health-library/treatments-and-procedures/carpal-tunnel-injection|archivedate=2015-07-10|deadurl=no|via=The Mount Sinai Hospital}}</ref>。但是這種治療不宜長期使用，有決定性的治療方案之後，通常便不再使用類固醇局部注射治療。皮質類固醇注射對於減慢疾病進展似乎不十分有效<ref name="Padua2016" />。

=== 手術 ===
{{main|{{le|腕隧道手術|Carpal tunnel surgery}}}}
手術切開[[橫腕韌帶|橫腕韌帶]]稱為腕隧道減壓手術。當出現持續的麻木、肌肉無力或萎縮，夜間副木或其他保守治療不再能控制原本的間歇性症狀時，則建議手術治療<ref name="Hui_2004">{{cite journal|title=Long-term outcome of carpal tunnel syndrome after conservative treatment|first1=A.C.F.|last2=Wong|first2=S.M.|journal=International Journal of Clinical Practice|issue=4|doi=10.1111/j.1368-5031.2004.00028.x|year=2004|volume=58|pages=337–9|pmid=15161116|last3=Tang|first3=A.|last4=Mok|first4=V.|last5=Hung|first5=L.K.|last6=Wong|first6=K.S.|last1=Hui}}</ref>。手術可以在[[局部麻醉|局部麻醉]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Open Carpal Tunnel Surgery for Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|url=http://www.webmd.com/pain-management/carpal-tunnel/open-carpal-tunnel-surgery-for-carpal-tunnel-syndrome|accessdate=July 9, 2015|website=WebMD|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707145827/http://www.webmd.com/pain-management/carpal-tunnel/open-carpal-tunnel-surgery-for-carpal-tunnel-syndrome|archivedate=July 7, 2015|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Youha">{{cite journal|title=Update/Review: Changing of Use of Local Anesthesia in the Hand|first1=Sarah|last2=Lalonde|first2=Donald|date=May 2014|journal=Plastic and Reconstructive Surgery Global Open|issue=5|doi=10.1097/GOX.0000000000000095|volume=2|pages=e150|pmc=4174079|pmid=25289343|last1=al Youha}}</ref><ref name="Nabhan">{{cite journal|title=Endoscopic Carpal Tunnel Release using a modified application technique of local anesthesia: safety and effectiveness|date=April 25, 2008|journal=Journal of Brachial Plexus and Peripheral Nerve Injury.|doi=10.1186/1749-7221-3-11|volume=3|pages=e35–e38|pmc=2383895|pmid=18439257|vauthors=Nabhan A, Ishak B, Al-Khayat J, ((Steudel W-I))|number=11}}</ref>或區域麻醉<ref name="AAOS">{{cite web|title=AAOS Informed Patient Tutorial – Carpal Tunnel Release Surgery|url=http://www5.aaos.org/icm/PrintModule.cfm?module=icm002|accessdate=July 9, 2015|publisher=The American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719060013/http://www5.aaos.org/icm/PrintModule.cfm?module=icm002|archivedate=July 19, 2015|dead-url=yes}}</ref>下進行，搭配使用<ref>{{cite journal|title=Remifentanil-Propofol Sedation as an Ambulatory Anesthesia for Carpal Tunnel Release|date=2010|journal=Journal of Korean Neurosurgical Society|issue=5|doi=10.3340/jkns.2010.48.5.429|volume=48|pages=429–433|pmc=3030083|pmid=21286480|vauthors=((Lee J-J)), Hwang SM, Jang JS, Lim SY, ((Heo D-H)), Cho YJ}}</ref>或不使用<ref name="Youha" />{{Le|鎮靜|Sedation}}輔助，或在[[全身麻醉|全身麻醉]]下進行<ref name="Nabhan" /><ref name="AAOS" />。一般而言，較輕症的病例可以保守治療控制數月至數年，但較嚴重的病例在症狀上沒有緩解，很可能導致需要手術治療<ref>{{cite journal|title=Long-term outcomes of symptomatic electrodiagnosed carpal tunnel syndrome|first1=JA|last2=Morita|first2=MP|journal=Arquivos de Neuro-Psiquiatria|issue=2A|doi=10.1590/S0004-282X2003000200007|year=2003|volume=61|pages=194–8|pmid=12806496|last3=Molina|first3=AF|last4=Zanetta|first4=DM|last5=Sato|first5=AK|last6=Rocha|first6=CE|last7=Fasanella|first7=CC|last1=Kouyoumdjian}}</ref>。

短期內（6個月）手術比裝具（須穿戴6週以上）有更好的療效，但是長期（12－18個月）來看，手術和裝具的療效相近<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Effectiveness of Passive Physical Modalities for the Management of Soft Tissue Injuries and Neuropathies of the Wrist and Hand: A Systematic Review by the Ontario Protocol for Traffic Injury Management (OPTIMa) Collaboration|first1=Kevin|last2=Sutton|first2=Deborah|journal=Journal of Manipulative and Physiological Therapeutics|issue=7|doi=10.1016/j.jmpt.2015.06.006|year=2015|volume=38|pages=493–506|pmid=26303967|last3=Côté|first3=Pierre|last4=Dion|first4=Sarah|last5=Wong|first5=Jessica J.|last6=Yu|first6=Hainan|last7=Randhawa|first7=Kristi|last8=Southerst|first8=Danielle|last9=Varatharajan|first9=Sharanya|last1=D'Angelo}}</ref>。

=== 物理治療 ===
{{main|{{le|腕隧道症候群的物理治療|Physical therapy in carpal tunnel syndrome}}}}
美國骨科醫學會制定的[[實證醫學|實證]]指南將[[物理治療|物理治療]]和其他非手術治療方式劃分為多個等級<ref>{{cite journal|title=American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons Clinical Practice Guideline on The Treatment of Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|last=Keith|first=M. W.|date=4 January 2010|journal=The Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery|issue=1|doi=10.2106/JBJS.I.00642|volume=92|pages=218–219|pmc=6882524|pmid=20048116|author3=Chung, K. C.|author4=Amadio, P. C.|author5=Andary, M.|author6=Barth, R. W.|author7=Maupin, K.|author8=Graham, B.|author9=Watters, W. C.|author10=Turkelson, C. M.|author12=Wies, J. L.|author13=McGowan, R.|author2=Masear, V.|author11=Haralson, R. H.}}</ref>。物理治療的主要問題之一是試圖要扭轉腕隧道內累積數年的病理變化，醫療從業人員警告：任何物理治療，如{{le|肌筋膜放鬆術|Myofascial release}}，可能需要持續數週才能產生療效<ref>{{cite journal|title=Osteopathic Manipulative Medicine for Carpal Tunnel Syndrome|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_jaoa-the-journal-of-the-american-osteopathic-association_2012-03_112_3/page/127|last=Siu|first=G.|date=1 March 2012|journal=The Journal of the American Osteopathic Association|issue=3|volume=112|pages=127–139|pmid=22411967|author3=Rafique, M.|author4=Weinik, M.M.|author2=Jaffee, J.D.}}</ref>。

有些文獻主張可以利用一些積極措施來減少腕部壓力並減輕疼痛，比如採用更符合[[人體工學|人體工學]]的工作環境和生活環境，例如將[[QWERTY鍵盤|QWERTY鍵盤]]變換為人體工學較優化的[[德沃夏克鍵盤|德沃夏克鍵盤]]，在早期的腕隧道症候群研究中常被認為是有益的，然而這些研究的一些[[元分析|元分析]]認為它們提供的證據有限<ref name="Lincoln_2000">{{cite journal|title=Interventions for the primary prevention of work-related carpal tunnel syndrome|first1=A|last2=Vernick|first2=JS|journal=American Journal of Preventive Medicine|issue=4 Suppl|doi=10.1016/S0749-3797(00)00140-9|year=2000|volume=18|pages=37–50|pmid=10793280|last3=Ogaitis|first3=S|last4=Smith|first4=GS|last5=Mitchell|first5=CS|last6=Agnew|first6=J|last1=Lincoln}}</ref><ref name="Verhagen_2006">{{cite journal|title=Ergonomic and physiotherapeutic interventions for treating work-related complaints of the arm, neck or shoulder in adults|first1=Arianne P|last2=Karels|first2=Celinde C|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=3|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD003471.pub3|year=2006|volume=3|pages=CD003471|pmid=16856010|last3=Bierma-Zeinstra|first3=Sita MA|last4=Burdorf|first4=Lex L|last5=Feleus|first5=Anita|last6=Dahaghin|first6=Saede SD|last7=De Vet|first7=Henrica CW|last8=Koes|first8=Bart W|last9=Verhagen|first9=Arianne P|editor1-last=Verhagen|editor1-first=Arianne P|last1=Verhagen}}</ref>。

肌腱神經滑行運動對腕隧道症候群似乎有幫助<ref>{{cite journal|title=Efficacy of tendon and nerve gliding exercises for carpal tunnel syndrome: a systematic review of randomized controlled trials.|first1=SD|date=August 2015|journal=Journal of Physical Therapy Science|issue=8|doi=10.1589/jpts.27.2645|volume=27|pages=2645–8|pmc=4563334|pmid=26357452|last1=Kim}}</ref>。

